%2Fliu-xiaobos-plea-for-the-human-spirit.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANo+Enemies%2C+No+Hatred\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-independent-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-independent_3-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Owen, Emily-Anne (12 April 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/no-enemies-no-hatred-selected-essays-and-poems-by-liu-xiaobo-edited-by-perry-link-tienchi-martin-7640218.html\">\"No Enemies, No Hatred: Selected Essays and Poems, By Liu Xiaobo, edited by Perry Link, Tienchi Martin-Liao and Liu Xiay Link, Tienchi Martin-Liao and Liu Xia; June Fourth Elegies, By Liu Xiaobo, trans. Jeffrey Yang\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Independent\" title=\"The Independent\">The Independent</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">16 July</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Independent&amp;rft.atitle=No+Enemies%2C+No+Hatred%3A+Selected+Essays+and+Poems%2C+By+Liu+Xiaobo%2C+edited+by+Perry+Link%2C+Tienchi+Martin-Liao+and+Liu+Xiay+Link%2C+Tienchi+Martin-Liao+and+Liu+Xia%3B+June+Fourth+Elegies%2C+By+Liu+Xiaobo%2C+trans.+Jeffrey+Yang&amp;rft.date=2012-04-12&amp;rft.aulast=Owen&amp;rft.aufirst=Emily-Anne&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Fbooks%2Freviews%2Fno-enemies-no-hatred-selected-essays-and-poems-by-liu-xiaobo-edited-by-perry-link-tienchi-martin-7640218.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANo+Enemies%2C+No+Hatred\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-smithpd-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-smithpd_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=